import { Box, Container, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function Form() {
    return (
        <Container maxWidth="xs">
            <form action="" method="post">
                <Box mb={2} mt={10}>
                    <TextField
                        label="Entrer votre nom"
                        variant="outlined"
                        name="username"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                </Box>
                <Box mb={5}>
                   <TextField
                    label="Entrer votre texte"
                    variant="outlined"
                    name="username"
                    multiline
                    rows={7}
                    fullWidth
                /> 
                </Box>
                
            </form>
        </Container>
    )
}
